# Do not commit ignored docs

If `/docs` (or `docs/**`) is listed in `.gitignore` or `.git/info/exclude`, **do not** commit files under `docs/`, including:

- `docs/superpowers/specs/*`
- `docs/superpowers/plans/*`

Do **not** weaken ignore rules (no `!/docs/superpowers/` exceptions, no `git add -f` on ignored docs) unless the user explicitly asks.

Write specs/plans locally when the workflow requires them; the user will add/commit them manually if needed.
